                            <comment id="12907381" author="jyoung" created="Wed, 8 Sep 2010 20:48:54 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Are you planning on creating the integer array once, by adding int[] cardinality to AbstractMatrix, or did you have another solution in mind?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
