&lt;p&gt;I just committed a change that allocates once, adding cardinality to AM and adding rowSize() and columnSize() to Matrix pretty much in &lt;br/&gt;
line with what you suggest.  That the code was ever otherwise was just something that I wouldn&apos;t have believed until a profiler stuffed&lt;br/&gt;
it into my face.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
